{"tid":1351530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你地識唔識分 咩叫分化 咩叫批評","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:06:06.000Z","uid":78349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6e819429aad073cda5c36583eea1dd0fd6d9e1d8","tid":1351530,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:40:47.000Z","msg":"睇完謝哂皮個po<br />\n發現<span style=\"color: red;\">每次有人提出對於一啲同你有同一個政治立場嘅人嘅批評</span>嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n就好快會有人撲出嚟同你講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勿分化</span><br />\n<br />\n好簡單<br />\n分化係挑起兩個陣營之間嘅仇恨<br />\n務求彼此之間敵視對方<br />\neg 所有香港女仔都係雞 都係貪錢<br />\n私樓係人生贏家 公屋出世就係一世窮撚<br />\n<br />\n批評 係講緊 佢今次有啲咩做錯左<br />\n下次有啲咩可以做得更加好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該你認清楚 勿分化唔係等於唔提出批評嘅藉口</span>"},{"pid":"7b3c9b94b2e07de3e73f32a64b5efd5a00d21ac3","tid":1351530,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4d3b9f25de31e3e8cff1ce4c0703a78c7406f6a3","tid":1351530,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd00365e0371c9bc8c71f32febc63da08db9f4f3","tid":1351530,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:06:06.000Z","msg":"agger"}]}